snippet.textDisplay:
what a brilliant composition. Have been listening to coke studio both india and pakistan ever since it started and without any doubt, one if the finest composition to ever come out of coke studio. The song also drives a point that if the words and the soul of the song are backed up by great vocals and the supporting music , it takes the whole composition to another level. 
This song in a way is true depiction of the state of our society and also just tells that love for each other should be driving point and not the differences and hatred for each other. Specific mention about the partition has been so beautifully put that it deserves a special mention. Kudos to Gurdass mann, Diljit Dosanjh and Composer Jatinder Shah and the whole Coke Studio Team !!!
